node.text:
@Nature’s wonders 🤯 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @tourfervor

Located along the floor of the Atlantic Ocean, the Mid-Atlantic Ridge is the most extensive chain of mountains of earth, but less than 10% of the range is actually visible for us. There are very few places where the range isn’t hidden, and Iceland is one of the only places where you can see and even stand on this breathtaking ridge. Would you visit this area?

📷 @zynl_ozturk
Video by Cografya Dünyası on YouTube
📍Iceland
